headline: Airlines halt Puerto Vallarta flights after violence following Mexican cartel leader's killing
summary: U.S. and Canadian airlines halted flights to Puerto Vallarta and Guadalajara in Mexico.

headline: 1 Nasdaq 100 Stock to Research Further and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: While the Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is filled with cutting-edge technology and consumer companies, not all are on solid footing. Some are dealing with declining demand, high costs, or regulatory pressures that could limit future upside.
